metadata.name: Useless Feelings
metadata.description:
10 editions each for 0.05ETH, all holders will have a chance to get this physical in their hands, and all others that collected this beautiful artwork will instantly be granted a FREE airdrop!

---

Artwork meaning

Feelings, always deserve to be listened to but are also the ones that make you feel down, are also the ones who make you an Human overall, mental health is a serious subject that everyone should care about because it's your mental strength that defines who you are, things are not meant to be easy but as soon that you embrace them and have the right mind set you will have everything in your hands to turn things as you desire, with hard work and the right motivation we are unbeatable...
